Metadata: Geoduck aquaculture: a sound science seminar (online video)

Flash movie that streams on WSG website of a seminar held in 2009 on geoduck aquaculture during Sound Science Seminar on Geoduck Aquaculture. Including "Geoduck Aquaculture Investigations in Puget Sound: Digging Deep for Answers" (Glenn Van Blaricom) and "Local Effects of Geoduck Aquaculture on a Meadow of Intertidal Eelgrass in Samish Bay, Washington" (Micah Horwith).
